<h3>Re: Language support bug</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>Hi,<br/>If command &quot;dpkg-reconfigure locales&quot; don&#039;t fix your problem, please read this: <a href="https://www.linuxbabe.com/desktop-linux/change-the-language-of-your-debian-system-from-english-to-chinese" rel="nofollow">https://www.linuxbabe.com/desktop-linux … to-chinese</a></p>
</div>
